                            <span class="icon"><i class="fas fa-link fa-sm"></i></span><a class="taglinks" href="https://anthrosource.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/jola.12258">Paper auf AnthroSource</a></span>
                          
                          <span class="tag is-primary">
                            <span class="icon"><i class="fas fa-link fa-sm"></i></span><a class="taglinks" href="https://anthrosource.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/15481395">Journal auf AnthroSource</a></span>
                          
