      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-3 is-hidden-touch ">
<div class="is-size-7 has-text-black">Schlagw√∂rter:<br /><span class="has-text-link">Aktuelles<br />Publikationen<br />Peer-Reviewed Papers<br />Special Issues</span></div>
<div class="is-size-7 has-text-black"><br />Links:<br /><a href="https://www.wsupress.wayne.edu/journals/detail/narrative-culture" class="has-text-primary">Journal Homepage</a><br /><a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/10.13110/narrcult.6.issue-1" class="has-text-primary">Ausgabe auf JSTOR</a></div>

